snippet.title: Vikings: War of Clans - The Battle Has Come
snippet.description:
Play Vikings: War of Clans for free on all devices:

Play on iOS → https://plrm.info/3K9Nr2Y
Play on Android → https://plrm.info/3Ka3spE
Play on PC → https://plrm.info/3CHkZAS

Vikings: War of Clans is the gateway to the harsh world of the Vikings, where blood freezes in the wind and boils in frantic battles. Here you can become a true Jarl! Rule a thousand-strong army of brave warriors, build a city worthy of songs, find loyal Clan allies and fight hundreds of sly and cruel enemies!

A true Viking’s heart craves the blood of foes and perilous ordeals. They are waiting for you in the world of Vikings: War of Clans!
